  1 -- O.o ... see remark after Def 7.31 ;-)
decreasing_by
  · sorry
  · sorry

/-- Quasi-Tableau from Def 7.31. Here we "start the construction", then use `Qchildren`.
No names for the nodes as we use an inductive type, so we just write `X` for `Δₓ` -/
